shows.title: Pregnant at 16
shows.plot_overview:
According to the Ministry of Health in Russia, there are 800 underage girls per 100,000 pregnant women. Most of them decide to keep the child, and this decision radically changes their lives: now they are not just teenage girls, they are young mothers.

In each episode, we will get acquainted with the story of one heroine: how it happened that she became pregnant, how her parents and future father will perceive the news about the child, how her life will change after childbirth and how she will
